1
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:04,680
Come on in.

2
00:00:05,160 --> 00:00:06,560
You are not leaving this time.

3
00:00:06,560 --> 00:00:07,560
This is our own house.

4
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:08,920
Just make yourself at home, okay?

5
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:09,360
Okay.

6
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:10,290
Here,

7
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:11,930
let me open the door for you.

8
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:14,360
Mr. Chen,

9
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:16,000
a new tenant?

10
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,240
Not at all.

11
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:19,120
This is... I am his son.

12
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:20,360
Yes, yes, yes.

13
00:00:20,360 --> 00:00:22,640
My son and daughter-in-law are back to see me.

14
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:23,960
Not bad, Chen.

15
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:25,400
You look so young,

16
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,730
yet your son is this big.

17
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:28,330
Ayu, you're off to work?

18
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:30,900
Qiangzi is playing bodyguard for Ayu again.

19
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Alright, come in.

20
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:38,280
You can stay here.

21
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:40,080
It's just a bit plain.

22
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:41,690
It's very good, Master.

23
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,800
I'll change the bedsheets for you.

24
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:44,200
No need.

25
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:45,040
I'll do it.

26
00:00:45,040 --> 00:00:45,880
Yes, let Aiyuan do it.

27
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:46,800
They're in the cabinet.

28
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:47,720
Okay.

29
00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:49,000
Go to the shop to eat.

30
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,200
You guys get some rest.

31
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:50,960
Alright, I'll go first.

32
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:51,640
Okay, Master.

33
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:52,080
Okay.

34
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:53,400
I'll come down and help later.

35
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:54,080
Get some rest.

36
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:54,440
Okay.

37
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:55,480
The keys are here.

38
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:56,320
Okay, Master.

39
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,250
I'm leaving now.

40
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,400
Sir, slow down.

41
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,760
You mean Hua Weihong,

42
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,960
with the long hair?

43
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:33,200
Cowardly and following me every day,

44
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,530
treating me as his boss?

45
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,400
Strictly speaking,

46
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:37,800
we are not very close.

47
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:39,800
What nonsense are you talking about?

48
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:40,560
Calm down.

49
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,440
Look at your sad faces.

50
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,920
Couldn't stand that guy's nonsense?

51
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:55,640
You are a girl.

52
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:58,000
Be elegant and don't be so impulsive.

53
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,040
I learned it from you.

54
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,240
When did I teach you that?

55
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,920
I have always enforced the law civilly.

56
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,200
If you don't believe me, ask Lin Wei.

57
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,130
Comrade Lin Wei,

58
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,759
you've been in our Guangnan police force for a while.

59
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,720
You always keep to yourself

60
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,040
and don't have a girlfriend.

61
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,440
I think our Comrade Zhang Ran

62
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:15,600
has a good figure and good looks.

63
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:16,930
You two are a good match.

64
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:22,570
Has anyone told you that you're funny?

65
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,160
No.

66
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:25,720
You will soon.

67
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:27,840
Brat.

68
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,220
You're laughing at me.

69
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:42,960
Honey,

70
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:44,840
how was today?

71
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,120
About the same as usual.

72
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,240
Always this amount.

73
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:47,770
Alright.

74
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,800
No, no, there's more.

75
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,120
We made a lot today.

76
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,720
Why is there so much money?

77
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,780
Your apprentice's wife gave it to me.

78
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,520
Who told you to accept it?

79
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,720
Why can't I accept it?

80
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,320
Look how much this is.

81
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:03,120
How many dishes would you have to cook to earn this?

82
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,320
This is inappropriate.

83
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,600
I'll return it tomorrow.

84
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:07,920
Give it back to me.

85
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,400
She gave it out of respect for me.

86
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,120
Being good to me is being good to you, isn't it?

87
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,580
We have to keep this money.

88
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:15,200
It's not easy for them to make money either.

89
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,440
Give it back to them.

90
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,000
I'll reward you with a bottle of liquor.

91
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,320
No, you...

92
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,120
Go, go drink.

93
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:21,920
Don't disturb me while I'm doing the accounts. Go.

94
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,520
What's wrong?

95
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,930
You must be tired recently.

96
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,960
Don't worry.

97
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:32,760
It's quite safe to lay low here

98
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:33,840
for a while.

99
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:41,480
How about I take you out to relax?

100
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,360
Where to?

101
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,490
To spend some money.

102
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:53,040
Better not.

103
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,400
It's dangerous outside.

104
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,680
What if the police find us?

105
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,640
They won't.

106
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,640
We'll go to places

107
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:02,090
where the police wouldn't expect us to be.

108
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:12,560
Silly, aren't all these things yours?

109
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:14,160
Why are you still searching?

110
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,800
There are only two of us.

111
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:20,240
Can we finish all these dishes you ordered?

112
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,040
We don't need to finish them.

113
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,760
Just taste a bite of each dish.

114
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,720
I'll order more of whichever is good.

115
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,280
Compared to these dishes,

116
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,040
this is the real deal.

117
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,560
Over 500 for this bottle.

118
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,320
But dressing like this,

119
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,159
are you used to it?

120
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,140
Let me tell you.

121
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:49,340
We are going to be people of this class in the future.

122
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:52,760
Before becoming high-class people, we must first learn.

123
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,480
Here, drink your coffee.

124
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:00,080
You need to add sugar to this.

125
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,080
Stir it.

126
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,120
Try it again.

127
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,200
Wake up. Time for breakfast.

128
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,960
Baby, why did you come back so late?

129
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,159
I missed you.

130
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,280
Are you tired?

131
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,760
Why is there so much today?

132
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:53,240
Guess who gave this.

133
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,600
Who gave it?

134
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,480
Those two next door.

135
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,360
Thank you.

136
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,600
Those two?

137
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:06,280
Are they that rich?

138
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,600
They went to our place today and ordered the most expensive liquor.

139
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,560
They even left a 100 tip.

140
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:17,360
Baby, I promise I won't let you work this hard anymore.

141
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,360
You've said that so many times.

142
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,280
Who believes you?

143
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:23,540
Go eat your breakfast and leave me alone.

144
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:58,200
Do you think it's useful for us to stay up like this?

145
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,480
It's fine. I know him.

146
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:05,880
He doesn't go anywhere unless he's on a mission. Don't worry.

147
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:11,060
What about you? Are you staying up like this just for your brother?

148
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,680
He... He must be a good cop.

149
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:22,940
He's a good cop.

150
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:23,610
Brother.

151
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:26,020
Brother, I passed the exam. Brother.

152
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,080
Brother.

153
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:43,760
Lin Wei.

154
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:48,080
I'm sorry.

155
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,250
Your brother, Lin Jian,

156
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,610
died in the line of duty.

157
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:17,930
University.

158
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:52,440
We have to leave.

159
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,900
We are wanted nationwide.

160
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,200
Master.

161
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,600
I've bought the groceries. Great.

162
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,480
You're back.

163
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,290
No rush. We'll eat soon.

164
00:08:59,480 --> 00:08:59,940
Master.

165
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,640
Aiyuan and I have something urgent to do, so we'll leave now.

166
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,480
What is it? Why the rush?

167
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,200
It's temporary.

168
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:08,000
Master, we'll come see you again when we have time.

169
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,080
Master.

170
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,720
When will it end?

171
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,980
Take care of yourself.

172
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:12,800
Soon.

173
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:13,800
Let's go.

174
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,800
Honey.

175
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,520
Ma'am, we'll get going.

176
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,680
Honey, look at this.

177
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,720
What's wrong?

178
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,080
Put it away.

179
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:30,560
Go upstairs.

180
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,560
Go upstairs.

181
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:43,780
Don't move.

182
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:44,960
Don't you move either.

183
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,280
Take out the money.

184
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:49,440
Hurry up.

185
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,640
Stop counting, give it all to me.

186
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,140
You have the money, let her go.

187
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,080
Give me the watch too.

188
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,840
Hurry.

189
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:03,240
Brother, I advise you not to take this watch.

190
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,370
Then you don't want your woman either.

191
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,000
I can tell you're not Old Chen's son.

192
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,760
You're not clean either, are you?

193
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,490
Don't call the police, hear me?

194
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:23,400
These things will serve as hush money,

195
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:25,570
so I won't go out and talk nonsense.

196
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:26,640
Aiyuan.

197
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,520
This little brat.

198
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,130
We better leave now.

199
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:34,840
No.

200
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,480
I have to get the watch back.

201
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,000
Stolen goods are sold quickly.

202
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,000
The police can easily track it down.

203
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,120
If they find us,

204
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,820
we might bring trouble to our master.

205
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,290
Wait here for me.

206
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,240
Look at this.
